scraped.description:
Features:
- Built-in sound absorption microphone, your voice can be heard clearly in 10 meters.
- Great quality and exquisite appearance.
- 1M pixels, high definition and true color images.
- Left & right 360 degrees and up & down 30 degrees rotatable, you can adjust the angle as you like.
- Specialized optical lens, high precision.Designed for both laptop and desktop.
- Auto white balance, auto color correction. Manual adjustable focal length.
- Support for Windows XP / win2003 / win7 / win8 /10/ Vista 32bit Macbook OS or latest.

Specifications:
- DSP chip: Driverless
- Image sensor: CMOS
- Lens: glass lens
- Focal length: 8mm-infinity
- High definition: 1M pixels
- Resolution: 1920*1080P
- Frame rate: 30fps
- Line length: 140cm

- Package content:
- 1 x Web Camera
- 1 x User Manual

Notes:
1. Manual measuring, please allow 1 ~ 3mm error,thank you.
2. Due to the difference between different monitors, the picture may not reflect the actual color of the item. We guarantee the style is the same as shown in the picture.1080P Web Cam HD Camera Webcam with Mic Microphone for Computer PC Laptop Notebook
scraped.title: 1080P Web Cam HD Camera Webcam with Mic Microphone for Computer PC Laptop Notebook
